Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.32,0:02:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好像是没有事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.95,0:02:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎也不在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.58,0:02:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…我倒觉得不是什么大事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.31,0:02:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打过手机了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像关机了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一…出了什么事的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.26,0:03:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不必那么担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我等一下  没头没脑地去找也不是办法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩托起火了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.39,0:03:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贷款还有很多没有付清呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过好像挺美的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.76,0:03:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还得去买女式自行车去打工…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汽油烧着了也不会爆炸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.64,0:03:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然了  那种事只有在电影里才会有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.25,0:03:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如干脆轰隆一下  然后一了百了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有钱叫出租车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题在于能不能叫到出租车
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比吕美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.92,0:04:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两个都没有受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不叫救护车没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.97,0:04:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.13,0:04:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像没有受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.69,0:05:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天要报告给警察  好好处理哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.62,0:05:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没有受伤真是不幸中的万幸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什么？老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让女人们在一起会更好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽给比吕美灌输些奇怪的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.45,0:06:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.24,0:06:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那难道是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比吕美和我是亲兄妹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.37,0:06:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.94,0:06:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.96,0:06:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事怎么可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.63,0:07:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好没有受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换衣服吧  我来帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事是不可能的  不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.16,0:07:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老妈  比吕美  你们在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定在吧  我进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老妈  我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.18,0:07:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我累了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服都脏兮兮的  我要换衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.92,0:07:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那过会儿再说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  妈妈你太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷轰丸登上后院的土堤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是  约有十米的巨大的土堤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.95,0:08:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那里看到的地面的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛就是地底一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在啄食饵食的地面看起来很凄惨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.92,0:08:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  飞翔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  到底怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷轰丸虽然是这样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那时肚子却咕噜咕噜地叫着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.43,0:08:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终  它决定今天还是放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定明天吃饱饵食后再去天空翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.47,0:09:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像还是飞不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.09,0:09:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.01,0:09:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.79,0:09:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比吕美  今天都吃些什么菜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么体贴人  一点都不像朋与
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.29,0:09:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:10:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好友是个如此震撼校园的大丑闻的主角
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这区区一介女子高中生角色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实也够呛的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  要是连你都在意的话该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为那样  我才没有面子的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.14,0:10:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事先告诉你一下消息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.11,0:10:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正在召开职员会议
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.07,0:10:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,题目是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于本校数一数二的高材生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.98,0:10:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篮球部的王牌  端庄秀丽并且眉清目秀的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一个意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.12,0:10:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,端庄秀丽和眉清目秀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.54,0:10:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算啦  吃饭吧吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.27,0:10:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  今天交换的份
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:10:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去了汤浅比吕美的事故现场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:10:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说4号那家伙也没受伤？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.61,0:11:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  真是个走运的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.47,0:11:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.17,0:11:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  仲上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.97,0:11:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是哥们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.03,0:11:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先回教室了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师都那样说了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.29,0:11:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高冈队长什么时候变成规章制度的维护者了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:12:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说停学那也是从明天才开始的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.56,0:12:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那请允许我也退出今天的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道你会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去陪着比吕美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.06,0:12:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比吕美和朋与的份也要给我算进去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  没有记错的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说「我喜欢乃绘」  还在这里写下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.85,0:13:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粗茶淡饭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.25,0:13:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打架咯  打架咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊  打死他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.61,0:14:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃绘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才真是把我吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.94,0:15:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥说停学一周
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了  搞出这么大的事故
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.84,0:15:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有必要道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了汤浅比吕美才打架的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.37,0:15:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.97,0:15:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  还好吗 地面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.49,0:15:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连环画的后续画好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要给你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:15:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.63,0:16:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比吕美是我们的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会负责管教她的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.53,0:16:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.46,0:16:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷轰丸不太容易飞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.67,0:16:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷轰丸也隐隐约约感觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上  即使从十米高的土堤上开始飞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是哪也去不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一直在装作不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.52,0:16:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么雷轰丸不面对现实？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:17:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是…害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.38,0:17:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.90,0:17:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不敢面对自己只是区区一只鸡这个现实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷轰丸其实从一开始就知道自己是飞不起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也指真一郎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.93,0:17:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什么  好疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.60,0:18:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎  你能飞翔的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是自己不知道而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.80,0:18:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.58,0:18:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你翱翔的地方不是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  乃绘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.35,0:19:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.25,0:19:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.55,0:19:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我和伯父伯母一起从学校回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.50,0:19:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去学校了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.44,0:19:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰…冰淇凌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.32,0:19:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在回家路上和伯母买的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.89,0:19:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎君的在冰箱里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我像个傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道没有那种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么「你是我丈夫的孩子」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.27,0:20:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些话都是骗人的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.15,0:20:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你见到不成体统的样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.02,0:20:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些话都是骗人的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.51,0:20:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前对你太刻薄了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来也知道伯母不喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.94,0:20:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.91,0:20:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人之间存在着称为缘分的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.13,0:20:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那个和这个是两码事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你忘记以前发生过的所有事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:20:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那的确是太自以为是了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.09,0:21:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里多待一会儿可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.35,0:21:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  那曲子我以前常听呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.09,0:21:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我像个傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.91,0:21:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你为我担心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.87,0:23:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.89,0:23:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么办
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.61,0:23:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渐渐地陷入其中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.69,0:23:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渐渐地  渐渐地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.65,0:23:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是该说谢谢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.64,0:23:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会全部处理好的
